{"tid":470490,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"★[片]支棍節-----支那速遞愛工作！","createTime":"2017-11-16T10:46:19.000Z","updateTime":"2017-11-16T15:41:37.000Z","uid":19454,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"22d9ffbcdf9b6de4559fe0403726f4ba88de2a7e","tid":470490,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-16T10:46:19.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">疑不滿雙 11 加班！速遞員粗暴狂踢包裹</span><br />\n<br />\n根據內地澎湃新聞報道，片中兩名速遞員為江蘇鹽城韻達快遞員工，在影片中，將包裹一腳一腳踢下車，而拍攝者更加以鼓勵，表示「用勁用勁」。報道指兩名速遞員，疑因不想早起加班，以粗暴的方式對待包裹，來宣洩不滿。<br />\n<br />\n韻達快遞表示二人確是公司員工，在雙 11 期間，要求員工早上 7 點提早上班，遲到者將要被罰款。兩人平時比較懶散，可能出於報復心理，所以惡意對待包裹。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=-S0FCDA2qMs\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3D-S0FCDA2qMs&d=pyhFcLNY2ka9NaFFh0ZNAi7PofNJLCAwyGXsi6MH%2FEQ%3D&h=c1cd72d9\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=-S0FCDA2qMs</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://resource01.ulifestyle.com.hk/res/v3/image/content/1945000/1946453/c_1024.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fresource01.ulifestyle.com.hk%2Fres%2Fv3%2Fimage%2Fcontent%2F1945000%2F1946453%2Fc_1024.jpg&h=3d741c14&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"e63bdc85e6213d795942b0876170f76ae4a6ee0d","tid":470490,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-16T10:48:38.000Z","msg":"link:<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://ezone.ulifestyle.com.hk/article/1946453?=v\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fezone.ulifestyle.com.hk%2Farticle%2F1946453%3F%3Dv&d=pyhFcLNY2ka9NaFFh0ZNAi7PofNJLCAwyGXsi6MH%2FEQ%3D&h=969ca3c3\" target=\"_blank\">https://ezone.ulifestyle.com.hk/article/1946453?=v</a>"},{"pid":"3cc35d222eec5f1f549a35b7e7987cbbbf14fcaf","tid":470490,"uid":90,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-16T10:49:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 支那人先會唔鍾意返工"},{"pid":"b792dc330e